Tolbase - TOL Graphic User Interface 
=========================================

Installation Instructions
=========================

This file describes how to install Tolbase package for Unix and Linux.
[See the file ./win/INSTALL for details on how to build under Windows.]

   All you have to do is (as root) "make install"
   
   Tolbase is a Tcl package that uses Toltcl Library and Tol Library. 
   This is the reason why these two packages have to be installed 
   previously on target system.
   The necessary files are installed under /usr/lib/tolbase1.1.2

   If you want to install tolbase under a different destination 
   directory, you can use "configure" script with the --prefix option.

